# eng.net planned package surface
#
# Purpose:
#   HTTP/download boundaries with explicit endpoint, cache, hash, fixture, and
#   reproducibility policy.
#
# Current implementation:
#   no native network module yet. Workflow examples use fixture files and
#   explicit process boundaries.
#
# Planned helper vocabulary:
#   http get
#   download
#   fixture fallback
#   require pinned hash
#
# Review contract:
#   method, URL, query, headers policy, cache key, expected hash, observed hash,
#   status, profile policy, and source span.
